02:22:59.000 --> 02:23:01.000
You get brief moments of blue;

02:23:01.000 --> 02:23:03.000
it looks like the weather
is a little clearer

02:23:03.000 --> 02:23:05.000
than you're used to seeing
in this vicinity.

02:23:05.000 --> 02:23:08.220
But the day is yours.
