from the servants. Cassandra says,

02:55:57.000 --> 02:56:00.000
"Well, thank you all for coming.

02:56:00.000 --> 02:56:04.000
"I believe there is much
to get underway here. This,"a

02:56:04.000 --> 02:56:09.000
MATT: And she gestures
towards Gilmore and Allura; they nod.

02:56:09.000 --> 02:56:13.000
Eskil raises his hand a moment.

02:56:13.000 --> 02:56:17.000
MATT: "So, while you've been gone.

02:56:17.000 --> 02:56:19.000
"Allura, you've been
doing this research for a bit."

02:56:19.000 --> 02:56:23.000
"Thank you, thank you.
So, we've been trying

02:56:23.000 --> 02:56:30.000
