03:12:03.000 --> 03:12:07.020
LAURA: You think there's something
bigger than Thordak in the Fire Plane?

03:12:07.020 --> 03:12:11.000
TALIESIN: I have terrible thoughts.
It's a terrible thought.

03:12:11.000 --> 03:12:13.000
MARISHA: I mean, I'm sure there is
something bigger than Thordak,

03:12:13.000 --> 03:12:16.000
probably in the Fire Plane,

03:12:16.000 --> 03:12:20.000
but the Fire Ashari closed the portal.

03:12:20.000 --> 03:12:22.000
TALIESIN: That may
not have been the portal.

03:12:22.000 --> 03:12:25.000
