03:12:25.000 --> 03:12:30.000
that Thordak came out of.
It ripped apart my entire--

03:12:30.000 --> 03:12:32.230
TALIESIN: That may just be
where he escaped.

03:12:32.230 --> 03:12:35.000
That power may still be flowing.

03:12:35.000 --> 03:12:40.440
MARISHA: Well, Allura, how did you
lock him in the Fire Plane to begin with?

03:12:40.440 --> 03:12:47.110
MATT: "Well, we had,
through clever subterfuge,

03:12:47.110 --> 03:12:51.020
"managed to have a member of our team

03:12:51.020 --> 03:12:56.000
"work as a follower of Thordak,

03:12:56.000 --> 03:13:00.000
"work into his greater trust

03:13:00.000 --> 03:13:04.000
"and convince him
that to perpetuate his wealth,

03:13:04.000 --> 03:13:07.000
"his growth, his strength,

03:13:07.000 --> 03:13:12.000
"that he needed to truly embrace
the essence of fire.

03:13:12.000 --> 03:13:16.000
