03:13:16.000 --> 03:13:20.650
"there are remnants of the First War

03:13:20.650 --> 03:13:22.990
"that exist in this world and others.

03:13:22.990 --> 03:13:26.000
"The very core
of the elemental chaos itself,

03:13:26.000 --> 03:13:29.000
"the hearts of the titans left behind.

03:13:29.000 --> 03:13:33.450
"These heart-stones are
the very basis,

03:13:33.450 --> 03:13:36.360
"or, at least,
shadows of the basis

03:13:36.360 --> 03:13:41.000
"of what made the elements
when creation came to be.

03:13:41.000 --> 03:13:45.000
"We had found one of these
on the Fire Plane,

03:13:45.000 --> 03:13:48.000
"but the nature of these
is that they cannot be removed.

03:13:48.000 --> 03:13:51.000
"If they are brought
beyond the plane themselves,

03:13:51.000 --> 03:13:54.000
