do weaken,

03:14:00.000 --> 03:14:02.000
"and those that attempted
to harness their power

03:14:02.000 --> 03:14:05.000
"leave it to ruin,
destroying all around them

03:14:05.000 --> 03:14:06.500
"before it whirls itself
into a frenzy

03:14:06.500 --> 03:14:12.000
"of uncontrollable arcane mass
and destroys everything nearby.

03:14:12.000 --> 03:14:13.500
"These were many of the fools

03:14:13.500 --> 03:14:17.000
"who ushered in the beginning
of the Second War.

03:14:17.000 --> 03:14:22.000
"So. Essentially,
we convinced Thordak

03:14:22.000 --> 03:14:24.000
"to find one of these in the plane

03:14:24.000 --> 03:14:26.850
"and convinced him
