all of our forces gathered

03:14:29.000 --> 03:14:33.000
"and we attacked him,
pressed him down,

03:14:33.000 --> 03:14:35.000
"and the gem
that we had convinced him--

03:14:35.000 --> 03:14:36.460
"the heart-stone
that we had convinced him

03:14:36.460 --> 03:14:39.000
"to take into himself,

03:14:39.000 --> 03:14:42.000
"well, we found a way to seal it,

03:14:42.000 --> 03:14:45.040
"to banish it permanently to that plane
