MATT: "But his mass,

03:15:37.670 --> 03:15:44.270
"his unforeseen size
to a creature like that.

03:15:44.270 --> 03:15:48.510
"I couldn't help but notice
that within his torso

03:15:48.510 --> 03:15:52.530
"there was a pulsing heart...

03:15:52.530 --> 03:15:55.790
"of red glass."

03:16:00.500 --> 03:16:02.000
LAURA: All right.

03:16:02.000 --> 03:16:04.000
