MATT: He looks over to Allura. 
Allura nods.

03:16:06.000 --> 03:16:08.000
"Well, if that is the case,
then it's, I think,

03:16:08.000 --> 03:16:10.000
"there's very much a chance

03:16:10.000 --> 03:16:14.000
"that he did escape
with the heart-stone intact."

03:16:14.000 --> 03:16:17.000
TRAVIS: I have a question.

03:16:17.000 --> 03:16:19.000
We've got one of the Vestiges

03:16:19.000 --> 03:16:24.000
in these Titanstone Knuckles,
