03:16:24.000 --> 03:16:27.000
If I left the plane with these,

03:16:27.000 --> 03:16:30.120
are they gonna blow everybody up?

03:16:30.120 --> 03:16:35.000
MATT: "An intact heart-stone
is the true source of power.

03:16:35.000 --> 03:16:38.610
"Those have been carved from one,
an inert one, or, at least,

03:16:38.610 --> 03:16:40.500
"they carry but a smidgen of the power.

03:16:40.500 --> 03:16:42.000
"I think you're safe, Grog."

03:16:42.000 --> 03:16:45.000
TRAVIS: Oh, thank god.
ASHLEY: Phew.

03:16:45.000 --> 03:16:47.000
LAURA: Which one?

03:16:47.000 --> 03:16:50.500
TRAVIS: Kord.
LAURA: Oh, Kord. I got it. (chuckles)

03:16:50.500 --> 03:16:51.970
MATT: Allura leans in again.

03:16:51.970 --> 03:16:57.000
"I have been keeping an eye on Emon
from this distance, as well.

03:16:57.000 --> 03:17:00.000
"It seems that Thordak's very essence

03:17:00.000 --> 03:17:02.000
"twists the land with elemental magic."

03:17:02.000 --> 03:17:03.460
TRAVIS: (whispering) Oh, shit.

03:17:03.460 --> 03:17:05.500
MATT: "My distant views of the city

03:17:05.500 --> 03:17:09.000
"have shown the center of the town
cracked with volcanic fire

03:17:09.000 --> 03:17:13.000
"as he digs and burrows
beneath the city itself."

03:17:13.000 --> 03:17:16.000
TALIESIN: (whispering) Fuck.
LAURA: Oh, fuck.

03:17:16.000 --> 03:17:18.000
TRAVIS: Wait, why is he
digging and burrowing?

03:17:18.000 --> 03:17:21.000
