as he sees fit.

03:17:21.000 --> 03:17:22.500
TRAVIS: Or is he looking for something?
LAURA: Because he's a dick.

03:17:22.500 --> 03:17:24.000
TRAVIS: Is he not
looking for something?

03:17:24.000 --> 03:17:26.000
TALIESIN: He might be
looking for something,

03:17:26.000 --> 03:17:27.500
or might be making--

03:17:27.500 --> 03:17:29.000
MARISHA: So these heart-stones

03:17:29.000 --> 03:17:33.310
embrace the essence 
of where they reside?

03:17:35.000 --> 03:17:39.000
MATT: "Their essence
is created where they reside."

03:17:39.000 --> 03:17:42.860
MARISHA: And he has the heart-stone
of the Fire Elemental Plane

03:17:42.860 --> 03:17:45.000
living inside of him.

03:17:45.000 --> 03:17:51.000
MATT: "A heart-stone. There are many."
MARISHA: A heart-stone. Right.

03:17:51.000 --> 03:17:52.500
LAURA: I'm confused.

03:17:52.500 --> 03:17:54.000
TRAVIS: I need more wine.

03:17:54.000 --> 03:17:55.500
Do you think he was
just making himself at home,

03:17:55.500 --> 03:17:58.000
or do you think he was
looking for something?

03:17:58.000 --> 03:18:00.500
MATT: "I don't know.
He seems pretty lax.

03:18:00.500 --> 03:18:02.000
"From what I could tell
from my investigations,

03:18:02.000 --> 03:18:04.000
"the major step
in the Conclave's plan

03:18:04.000 --> 03:18:06.000
"is already over."

03:18:06.000 --> 03:18:07.500
LAURA: Take over everything.

03:18:07.500 --> 03:18:09.650
MATT: "Now they settle
into the divided territories

03:18:09.650 --> 03:18:12.000
"and forget each other.

03:18:12.000 --> 03:18:15.810
"Now, I feel that Thordak
is far too old and covetous

03:18:15.810 --> 03:18:19.000
"to be content with just Emon.

03:18:19.000 --> 03:18:22.000
"Now, this was vengeance,
which is now complete.

03:18:22.000 --> 03:18:24.500
"Who knows what the next stage
in his terrible design is."

03:18:24.500 --> 03:18:26.000
MARISHA: So you're thinking

03:18:26.000 --> 03:18:29.000
the Chroma Conclave
was simply a temporary alliance?

03:18:29.000 --> 03:18:32.000
MATT: "There are very few

03:18:32.000 --> 03:18:35.500
"permanent alliances 
between chromatic dragons."

03:18:35.500 --> 03:18:37.550
LAURA: Well, that's good.
MARISHA: We can use this.

03:18:37.550 --> 03:18:40.000
LAURA: Maybe they won't take vengeance.

03:18:40.000 --> 03:18:42.000
ASHLEY: Maybe we can get one of them
on our side.

03:18:42.000 --> 03:18:44.000
TALIESIN: We can only be so hopeful
that they tear each other apart.

03:18:44.000 --> 03:18:49.000
LAURA: Maybe the white one will want
to help kill Thordak with us.

03:18:49.000 --> 03:18:53.000
