03:19:09.500 --> 03:19:11.000
LAURA: Shit.
TRAVIS: Seize.

03:19:11.000 --> 03:19:13.000
MARISHA: So we can take-- yeah.

03:19:13.000 --> 03:19:17.000
LAURA: If we can pry it
out of his body,

03:19:17.000 --> 03:19:18.500
