03:20:18.000 --> 03:20:23.000
"but me and Drake
are working on some ideas. (sighs)"

03:20:23.000 --> 03:20:25.870
MARISHA: Do you know exactly how
these heart-stones are forged?

03:20:25.870 --> 03:20:30.000
MATT: "They're not forged.
They existed.

03:20:30.000 --> 03:20:32.000
"They were the hearts
of the primordial titans

03:20:32.000 --> 03:20:35.000
"that existed on this world
before the gods even came here."

03:20:35.000 --> 03:20:37.000
MARISHA: Oh, that's right.
LAURA: Wow.

03:20:37.000 --> 03:20:40.120
MATT: "They were the true denizens
of this world, before any of us."

03:20:44.000 --> 03:20:48.000
SAM: This is an awesome dinner,
