LAURA: This wine is pretty good.
ASHLEY: It's very good.

03:20:58.000 --> 03:21:01.000
MATT: "Perhaps rest is in order
for all of us.

03:21:01.000 --> 03:21:03.580
"It's been a lot. I'm so sorry.
