03:22:00.410 --> 03:22:03.560
MATT: "Object impermanence.
(glug glug)

03:22:03.560 --> 03:22:06.500
"Next time you're going there,
you tell me."

03:22:06.500 --> 03:22:08.000
LAURA: Oh, yes. We will.

03:22:08.000 --> 03:22:10.000
TALIESIN: We will be returning.

03:22:10.000 --> 03:22:13.000
TRAVIS: On one condition.
