03:22:23.000 --> 03:22:25.000
She reaches out
and smacks your cheek.

03:22:25.000 --> 03:22:27.000
TRAVIS: Yeah.

03:22:27.000 --> 03:22:29.000
(laughter)

03:22:29.000 --> 03:22:32.000
MATT: "All right, kiddies,
sleep it is."

