MATT: All righty.

03:34:49.270 --> 03:34:51.500
LIAM: That was super awesome
and I can't wait to see the outcome,

03:34:51.500 --> 03:34:53.000
but before that happens,

03:34:53.000 --> 03:34:56.450
I was standing right here
when these two walked off,

03:34:56.450 --> 03:35:03.000
so I am waiting in the exact same spot
for my sister to return.

03:35:03.000 --> 03:35:04.500
MATT: A lot of time passes.
LIAM: It's fine.

03:35:04.500 --> 03:35:06.000
MATT: A few hours pass
before she returns,

03:35:06.000 --> 03:35:08.310
but she eventually does.

03:35:08.310 --> 03:35:11.000
LAURA: Are you still here?
You should go to bed.

03:35:11.000 --> 03:35:14.000
LIAM: I will.
I took a little bit of a nap.

03:35:14.000 --> 03:35:16.000
LAURA: In the dining hall?

03:35:16.000 --> 03:35:18.000
LIAM: Yeah.

03:35:18.000 --> 03:35:19.740
LAURA: What?

03:35:23.000 --> 03:35:25.960
LIAM: You're a grown-ass woman,
and you're twice as strong as I am.

03:35:25.960 --> 03:35:26.830
LAURA: I know.

03:35:26.830 --> 03:35:29.980
LIAM: So your business is your business.

03:35:29.980 --> 03:35:34.460
Just... both eyes open, yeah?

03:35:34.460 --> 03:35:40.590
LAURA: Always. (chuckles)
I'm very perceptive.

03:35:42.000 --> 03:35:44.000
LAURA: (cackles)
LIAM: Don't do that to me.

03:35:44.000 --> 03:35:45.960
TALIESIN: That's two.
Two winks! Ah hah hah.

03:35:45.960 --> 03:35:48.490
LIAM: Please don't ever
do that to me again.

03:35:48.490 --> 03:35:51.000
LAURA: I love you so much.

03:35:51.000 --> 03:35:55.020
LIAM: And if you do, you will 
never use that wink on me again.

03:35:55.020 --> 03:35:57.000
It is not for me.

03:35:57.000 --> 03:35:58.560
LAURA: All right.

03:35:58.560 --> 03:36:04.000
LIAM: Just... he's charming,
but both eyes open, please.

03:36:04.000 --> 03:36:05.500
LAURA: I don't know
what you are talking about.

03:36:05.500 --> 03:36:06.740
LIAM: Yeah, the fuck you don't.

03:36:06.740 --> 03:36:10.020
I'm going to go to my room now
and see if I splat on the floor.

