LIAM: What are you doing?
TALIESIN: Wow.

03:43:25.000 --> 03:43:26.700
MATT: What a rakshasa does.
SAM: Good job, man.

03:43:26.700 --> 03:43:28.500
LAURA: Oh my god.
MARISHA: What the fuck?!

03:43:28.500 --> 03:43:29.500
TALIESIN: Wow.

03:43:29.500 --> 03:43:31.500
MARISHA: Has he been a rakshasa 
